@startuml l3_activity
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title **Level 3 — Activity Diagram (Five-Agent Pipeline)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager (qwen3:8b)|
:Decompose question into\nworkstreams & sub-questions;
:Create analysis plan (JSON);
note right
  **Tools:** none
  **Cannot:** research, analyze, write report
end note

|#E8F5E9|Market Researcher (qwen3:14b)|
:Receive question + analysis plan;
:Research loop (max 8 rounds):\nsearch_web() → read_document();
:Synthesize into Market Analysis JSON;
note right
  **Tools:** search_web(), read_document()
  **Cannot:** do financials, assess risks
end note

|#FFF3E0|Financial Analyst (deepseek-r1:14b)|
:Receive plan + market analysis;
:Model costs, revenue, ROI,\nbreak-even, sensitivity analysis;
:Use chain-of-thought reasoning\n(explicit <think> tags);
:Produce Financial Analysis JSON;
note right
  **Tools:** none (native reasoning)
  **Cannot:** do market research, assess risks
end note

|#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst (qwen3:14b)|
:Receive plan + market +\nfinancial analysis;
:Research risks: search_web()\n+ read_document() + assess_risk();
:Identify 5-8 risks with\nprobability × impact scoring;
:Produce Risk Assessment JSON;
note right
  **Tools:** search_web(), read_document(),
  assess_risk()
  **Cannot:** do market research, financials
end note

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant (qwen3:32b)|
:Receive all prior analyses;
:Synthesize into consulting report\nwith 2-3 strategic options,\npros/cons, recommendation;
:Stream report tokens via SSE;
note right
  **Tools:** none (reads context only)
  **Cannot:** search for new information
end note

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator (gemini-2.5-flash)|
:Score report on 6-criterion rubric;
:Produce evaluation scorecard;

|Client|
:Receive report + scorecard;
stop

@enduml
